ss Events and Trends", "bbox": [96.9, 810.2, 358.2, 831.0]}, {"text": "Products. We design, manufacture and market da Vinci Surgical Systems, which are advanced surgical systems that we believe represent a new", "bbox": [118.8, 840.5, 1138.2, 860.6]}, {"text": "generation of surgery. We believe that this new generation of surgery, which we call da Vinci surgery, is a significant advancement similar in scope to previous", "bbox": [75.0, 862.4, 1187.3, 882.4]}, {"text": "generations of surgery—open surgery and minimally invasive surgery, or conventional MIS. The da Vinci Surgical System consists of a surgeon’s console, or", "bbox": [75.0, 884.3, 1192.9, 904.3]}, {"text": "consoles, a patient-side cart and a high performance vision system. The da Vinci Surgical System translates the surgeon’s natural hand movements, which are", "bbox": [75.0, 906.2, 1193.0, 926.2]}, {"text": "performed on instrument controls at a console, into corresponding micro-movements of instruments positioned inside the patient through small incisions, or", "bbox": [75.0, 928.5, 1165.1, 948.0]}, {"text": "ports. We believe that the da Vinci Surgical System provides the surgeon with intuitive control, range of motion, fine tissue manipulation capability and high", "bbox": [75.0, 949.9, 1175.5, 970.0]}, {"text": "definition 3-D vision, while simultaneously allowing the surgeons to work through the small ports of MIS.", "bbox": [75.0, 972.3, 819.7, 991.8]}, {"text": "By placing computer-enhanced technology between the surgeon and the patient, we believe that the  da Vinci Surgical System enables surgeons to deliver", "bbox": [118.8, 1009.3, 1183.0, 1029.4]}, {"text": "higher value minimally invasive surgical procedures to their patients. We model patient value as equal to: procedure efficacy / invasiveness. Here procedure", "bbox": [75.0, 1030.6, 1184.1, 1051.4]}, {"text": "efficacy is a", "bbox": [75.0, 1052.8, 159.2, 1073.2]}, {"text": "40", "bbox": [626.8, 1092.8, 642.3, 1110.1]}]}